8
00:02:58,778 --> 00:03:02,581
<i>It's Andy Walton and Clayton
stone neck and neck here today.</i>

9
00:03:06,085 --> 00:03:07,152
Yeah, Clayton!

10
00:03:07,154 --> 00:03:09,788
Come on, Andy.
Come on.

11
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:11,023
