945
01:13:50,927 --> 01:13:52,560
Hey, hey.

946
01:13:53,829 --> 01:13:56,030
So what?

947
01:13:57,032 --> 01:13:59,834
No matter what Trent wrote,

948
01:13:59,836 --> 01:14:02,403
