963
01:15:39,434 --> 01:15:42,303
That's why.

964
01:15:42,305 --> 01:15:44,272
It's a mine, mark.

965
01:15:47,543 --> 01:15:49,610
It's a gold mine.

966
01:15:53,181 --> 01:15:54,782
That is what he meant
when he said,

967
01:15:54,784 --> 01:15:56,317
